name: Unframed 11" x 14" Family Tree Art - Of Another Shape
description:
All pricing for "Family Tree Art of Another Shape" is negotiated and confirmed before art is rendered.  

Pricing based on simplicity of shape, intricacy and form.  The price is also based on size of finished artwork and whether or not you choose to have your custom piece framed.  

I have created Family Tree Art of Another Shape to form that of a company logo.  Imagine the possibilities.

Family Tree Art Possibilities:

Heart
Bust
Book
Ship
Animal Shape
Lighthouse
Piano 
Letter
Company Logo Shape   

Go to the "Contact Donna" page and let's get started.  Let me know what you are hoping to create and we can begin the process from there. 

Another consideration is creating a piece and selling the "artwork" by way of a .jpeg file where as a company you can use the finished piece when printing company t-shirts, note pads, coffee mugs etc.

JPEG File Format* If your desire is to have a piece created in this media, we would need to further discuss your expectations and from there I can provide a quote.    

Please read the entire "Order Process" page for further details on ordering your Family Tree Art Of Another Shape and obtaining the order form to get the artwork underway. 

Go to the "Contact Donna" if you have any questions or specifications.
